nad error typeclasses, and streaming and web socket capability definitions. This artifact is the Scala 3 JVM build of that shared foundation, enabling sttp client, tapir, model, and related modules to express effects, streams, and request and response metadata consistently.\\\",\\n./metadata/com.monovore/decline-effect_3/index.json:9:    \\\"description\\\" : \\\"Decline Effect adds Cats Effect integration to the decline command-line parser for Scala. It provides CommandIOApp so applications can define composable CLI parsers with decline and execute commands as cats-effect IO programs.\\\",\\n./metadata/org.typelevel/cats-effect_3/index.json:5:    \\\"source-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo.maven.apache.org/maven2/org/typelevel/cats-effect_3/$version$/cats-effect_3-$version$-sources.jar\\\",\\n./metadata/org.typelevel/cats-effect_3/index.json:6:    \\\"repository-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/typelevel/cats-effect\\\",\\n./metadata/org.typelevel/cats-effect_3/index.json:7:    \\\"test-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/typelevel/cats-effect/tree/v$version$/tests\\\",\\n./metadata/org.typelevel/cats-effect_3/index.json:8:    \\\"documentation-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/typelevel/cats-effect/tree/v$version$/docs\\\",\\n./metadata/org.typelevel/cats-effect_3/index.json:53:    \\\"source-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/typelevel/cats-effect_3/2.5.1/cats-effect_3-2.5.1-sources.jar\\\",\\n./metadata/org.typelevel/cats-effect_3/index.json:54:    \\\"repository-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/typelevel/cats-effect\\\",\\n./metadata/org.typelevel/cats-effect_3/index.json:55:    \\\"test-code-url\\\" : \\\"https://github.com/typelevel/cats-effect/tree/v2.5.1/core/shared/src/test/scala\\\",\\n./metadata/org.typelevel/cats-effect_3/index.json:56:    \\\"documentation-url\\\" : \\\"https://repo1.maven.org/maven2/org/typelevel/cats-effect_3/2.5.1/cats-effect_3-2.5.1-javadoc.jar\\\",\\n./metadata/org.typelevel/munit-cats-effect_3/index.json:5:    